    "title": "京东开放平台个人/个体店影音影像品类招商激励政策（2026.4.1-2026.6.30）",
    "followRuleId": "1358733517322432512",
    "content": "<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">为鼓励商家在京东开放平台个人/个体店积极经营影音影像品类，特制定激励政策，具体内容如下：</span></p>\n<h1 style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">一、参与商家</span></strong></h1>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">需要满足：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">京东开放平台以下指定<strong>类目</strong>的<strong>个人/个体</strong>店铺，且<strong>店铺入驻时间</strong>在2026.4.1-2026.6.30之内</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">指定类目：</span></strong></p>\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; line-height: 2;\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 75.0pt; background: #DC1623; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"100\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">一级类目</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 75.0pt; background: #DC1623; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"100\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">二级类目</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 83.25pt; background: #DC1623; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"111\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">三级类目</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 75.0pt; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" rowspan=\"10\" width=\"100\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">数码</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 75.0pt; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" rowspan=\"2\" width=\"100\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">影音娱乐</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 83.25pt; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"111\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">无线/蓝牙耳机</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 83.25pt; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"111\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">有线耳机</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 75.0pt; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" rowspan=\"8\" width=\"100\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">摄影摄像</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 83.25pt; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"111\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">摄像机</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 83.25pt; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"111\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">数码相框</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 83.25pt; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"111\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">单反配件</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 83.25pt; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"111\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">户外器材</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 83.25pt; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"111\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">影棚器材</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 83.25pt; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"111\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">全景相机</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 83.25pt; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"111\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">冲印服务</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 83.25pt; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"111\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">云台相机</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">注：店铺ID归属于京喜事业部下，具体店铺归属请咨询各店铺/类目运营（heshuoshuo1@jd.com），政策考核期内数据最终以平台数据为准。</span></p>\n<h1 style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">二、激励政策</span></strong></h1>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、店铺入驻时间：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2026.4.1-2026.6.30</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、店铺考核期：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">店铺<strong>入驻月</strong>起3个自然月</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">（15号前算当月入驻，15号后&amp;含15号算次月入驻）</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">3</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、激励规则：</span></strong></p>\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; line-height: 2;\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 75.0pt; background: #DC1623; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"100\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">入驻日期</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 75.0pt; background: #DC1623; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"100\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">店铺类型</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 132.0pt; background: #DC1623; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"176\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">三级类目</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 75.0pt; background: #DC1623; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"100\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">运营服务支持费率</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 96.35pt; background: #DC1623; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"128\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">考核期累计GMV达成</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 75.4pt; background: #DC1623; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"101\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">返还比例</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 75.0pt; background: #DC1623; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"100\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">返还方式</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 75.0pt; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" rowspan=\"3\" width=\"100\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2026.4.1-2026.6.30</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 75.0pt; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" rowspan=\"3\" width=\"100\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">个人/个体店</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 132.0pt; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" rowspan=\"2\" width=\"176\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">无线/蓝牙耳机、有线耳机</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 75.0pt; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" rowspan=\"2\" width=\"100\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2%-5.5%</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 96.35pt; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"128\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">&gt;30</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">万</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 75.4pt; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"101\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">实付运营服务支持费*100%</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 75.0pt; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"100\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">现金</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 96.35pt; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"128\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">&gt;6</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">万</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 75.4pt; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"101\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">实付运营服务支持费*50%</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 75.0pt; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"100\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">现金</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 132.0pt; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"176\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">摄像机、数码相框、单反配件、户外器材、影棚器材、全景相机、冲印服务、云台相机</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 75.0pt; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"100\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2%-3.5%</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 96.35pt; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"128\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">&gt;3</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">万</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 75.4pt; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"101\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">实付运营服务支持费100%</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 75.0pt; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"100\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">现金</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">*</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">示例1：蓝牙/无线耳机商家A入驻日期为2026年4月19日（15日后），则商家A入驻月份为5月，经营该类目的商品运营服务支持费率为2%，商家A在5、6、7月累计GMV达成16万元，可返还160000*2%*50%=1600元。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">*</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">示例2：影棚器材商家B入驻日期为2026年4月3日（15日前），则商家B入驻月份为4月，经营该类目的商品运营服务支持费率为2%，商家B在4月、5月、6月三个月累计GMV5万元，可返还50000*2%*100%=1000元。</span></p>\n<h1 style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">三、政策说明</span></strong></h1>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、返还形式：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">激励考核结束后，返还至商家钱包。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、GMV：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">考核期内店铺内下单且在次月前完成的订单产生的GMV【仅限政策参与商家在政策适用范围内的店铺ID产生的政策参与类目商品订单的GMV，且剔除退货、刷单等风控订单、优惠券金额等】，考核周期结束后，次月进行数据计算。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">3</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、统计周期：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2026</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">年4月1日-2026年6月30日期间启用的店铺方可参与本激励，店铺考核期结束后次月进行激励结算。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">4</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、首次入驻口径说明：</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">① </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">若同一主体前期曾开通过上述类目的店铺，且目前店铺正常经营，则不属于首次入驻，无法享受激励政策；</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">② </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">若同一主体前期曾开通过上述类目的店铺，但已关店停止经营，激励周期内重新启用或开设新店铺，可享受激励政策。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">5</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、运营服务支持费率：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">查询地址<a style=\"color: #467886; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://finance-temp-page-pro.pf.jd.com/CateGoryPoint\"><strong>https://finance-temp-page-pro.pf.jd.com/CateGoryPoint</strong></a>，必须按照主体类型+经营类目+品牌进行查询，满足运营服务支持费率限定范围内的商品订单可享受激励政策。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">6</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、激励考核周期内，若商家中途关店则激励终止。</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">7</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、核算激励时，若店铺经营状态为关闭，则不返还激励。</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">8</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、店铺销售非全新商品的，不可参与此激励。</span></strong></p>\n<h1 style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">四、违约责任</span></strong></h1>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">若商家在激励周期内发生以下任一情形，则京东开放平台有权取消商家因此获得的全部激励且不承担任何责任，如激励已发放，则京东开放平台有权自任意一笔待与商家及/或商家关联方结算的款项、已缴纳的保证金中直接扣除，不足抵扣的，京东开放平台有权保留继续追偿的权利。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、商家及其关联方采取不正当手段（如刷单、套券等）获取激励的行为；</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、商家存在恶意竞争、影响消费者权益、影响京东平台声誉等违反市场公平竞争原则、诚实信用原则、公序良俗的行为；</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">3</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、商家存在商品错挂、乱挂、销售二手等不合规经营的行为；</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">4</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、违反<a style=\"color: #467886; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=2614\">《京东开放平台招商资质标准细则》</a>的行为；</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">5</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、违反<a style=\"color: #467886; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=2754\">《京东开放平台商家违规管理总则》</a>的行为；</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">6</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、违反其他京东平台规则的行为。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p>",
